  "body": "### Description\r\nAs a consensus layer, I want Besu to fail when syncing a chain that does not reach the finalized block I announced so that potential problems can be caught early. \r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n* Backwards Sync syncs correctly when chain is descending from the finalized block\r\n* Backwards Sync throws an exception when the chain is not descending from the current finalized block.\r\n\r\n**Actual behaviour:** \r\n\r\nCurrently, BWS syncs even when under the finalized block and stops only when reaching a node that is already known.\r\n",
